articles.description: Members of the Michigan State faculty voted 61-4 to express no confidence in the eight-member governing body at the university. Meanwhile, the institution's interim president wrote to the campus community about cooperation with ongoing investigations.
articles.headline: Michigan State faculty delivers no-confidence vote on board of trustees

images.caption: The Michigan State faculty's vote against the board of trustees came largely in response to the board's decision to name John Engler the school's interim president.
images.name: John Engler [600x400] - Copy (2)

images.caption: Michigan State students, including one who jumped onto and sat on the middle of a table, interrupt an MSU board of trustees meeting to protest the school's selection of John Engler as the interim president.
images.name: MSU students vent frustration over interim president selection

videos.description: Keith Stone finds Kevarrius Hayes who softly slams home a dunk.
videos.headline: Gators' Hayes with easy two-handed jam.

videos.description: Yante Maten misses the jumper, but Rayshaun Hammonds doesn't give up on the play and tips it in.
videos.headline: Georgia's Hammonds keeps it a close game with tip shot

videos.description: Juwan Parker drains a 3-pointer from the wing to give Georgia their first lead of the game.
videos.headline: Big time triple made by Bulldogs' Parker

videos.description: Jalen Hudson opens the second half with back-to-back 3-pointers.
videos.headline: Florida's Hudson swishes in triples

videos.description: Chris Chiozza with a no-look pass to KeVaughn Allen who slams it home for a two-handed jam.
videos.headline: Gators' Allen throws down the hammer

videos.description: Jordan Harris goes in for the drive and lays one in with an up-and-under move.
videos.headline: Bulldogs' Harris ties game with up-and-under layup

videos.description: Bulldogs' Yante Maten attempts to make a jumper shot, but Keith Stone swats the ball away.
videos.headline: Florida's Stone stays with play and gets block

videos.description: Georgia forward Yante Maten talks about his second-half performance vs. Florida and what the Bulldogs need to do to build off their win.
videos.headline: Maten: Bulldogs finding ways to win
